data.description:
ASSUMABLE MORTGAGE AT 3% FOR QUALIFIED FHA BUYERS. REACH OUT WITH ANY QUESTIONS... BEAT THE MARKET RATE!

Welcome to this exquisite SMART HOME Aurora residence where a harmonious blend of modern updates and timeless elegance awaits. All three bathrooms have been masterfully remodeled, showcasing high-end fixtures and tasteful finishes that add a touch of luxury to your daily routine. These spa-like retreats will become your haven of relaxation. The kitchen has undergone a complete makeover, boasting stunning granite countertops that not only enhance functionality but also bring an air of sophistication to your culinary endeavors. The deep sink is a practical and stylish addition, making meal preparation and cleanup effortless. The refurbished hardwood floors throughout the home add warmth and charm, creating a seamless connection between classic and contemporary design. For those who love to entertain, a well-appointed wet bar provides an ideal space to host gatherings, mix drinks, and entertain with flair. Beyond the interiors, the spacious backyard is a haven for outdoor enjoyment. This space is perfect for year-round relaxation and recreation. Smart Home includes: Smart Lighting, Thermostat, Speakers, Alarm, Floodlight Cameras, and Lock!

With the Light Rail and I-225 only minutes away, there is an ease to commutes for anyone. Here is that quiet neighborhood with lots of parks close by you have been looking to enjoy and schools so close that are so close your kids can walk with ease.
